data.description: Motivated Sellers! What an amazing opportunity to own a beautiful, very well maintained home with 29 acres of land! If you are a hunter or just have an appreciation for nature this is a must see. 3 bedrooms (could be 4 with a closet upstairs) 1 bath and a 2 1/2 car garage. The west side of the property has 2 slabs, 69 x 14.5, and 24 x 8 for additional construction. This property features ponds and an abundance of wildlife. The home was completely remodeled in 2014, the roof replaced 2019. Located in Marshall school district, close to I 94, this home is priced to sell! Call Mike Palmer at 269-580-1515 for more information.
